data.value: Here you can find all the lessons that will prepare you and help you to better understand some of the most important foundations of mathematics. The Grade 9 Lessons focus on manipulating expressions and solving equations, which leads up to the equation of a line. Students then use the information and techniques they learned in Grade 9 and apply them to more complex problems one would find in Grade 10. The lessons for Grade 10 focus more on quadratics and learning about behaviour of graphs and functions.
